    "result": {"data":{"cur":{"id":"991a3c2f-b89a-58ad-a551-9d266eb3926b","html":"","excerpt":"","frontmatter":{"date":"March 14, 2022","title":"영화 리뷰 어플리케이션","categories":"프로젝트 featured","author":"웅스노트","emoji":"📽️"},"fields":{"slug":"/review/sparta-app/"}},"next":{"id":"f90765c4-e098-567a-8c9f-53343e689d47","html":"<h2 id=\"1-문제-설명\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\" aria-label=\"1 문제 설명 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 문제 설명</h2>\n<p>새로 생긴 놀이기구는 인기가 매우 많아 줄이 끊이질 않습니다.</p>\n<p>이 놀이기구의 원래 이용료는 price원 인데,</p>\n<p>놀이기구를 N 번 째 이용한다면 원래 이용료의 N배를 받기로 하였습니다.</p>\n<p>즉, 처음 이용료가 100이었다면 2번째에는 200, 3번째에는 300으로 요금이 인상됩니다.</p>\n<p>놀이기구를 count번 타게 되면 현재 자신이 가지고 있는 금액에서 얼마가 모자라는지를</p>\n<p>return 하도록 solution 함수를 완성하세요.</p>\n<p>(단, 금액이 부족하지 않으면 0을 return 하세요.)</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-제한-사항\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%9C-%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\" aria-label=\"2 제한 사항 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 제한 사항</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>놀이기구의 이용료 price : 1 ≤ price ≤ 2,500, price는 자연수</li>\n<li>처음 가지고 있던 금액 money : 1 ≤ money ≤ 1,000,000,000, money는 자연수</li>\n<li>놀이기구의 이용 횟수 count : 1 ≤ count ≤ 2,500, count는 자연수</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-풀이\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4\" aria-label=\"3 풀이 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 풀이</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Solution</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span> <span class=\"token function\">solution</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> price<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> money<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> count<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n     <span class=\"token comment\">//초기화</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span> answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">long</span> payment <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        \r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//지불 금액 계산</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span>count<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            payment <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>price<span class=\"token operator\">*</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//지불 금액(payment)과 소지 금액(money) 비교</span>\r\n        answer <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>money <span class=\"token operator\">></span> payment<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> payment <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> money<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//결과값 리턴</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> answer<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1-%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85\">1. 문제 설명</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2-%EC%A0%9C%ED%95%9C-%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\">2. 제한 사항</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3-%ED%92%80%EC%9D%B4\">3. 풀이</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 14, 2022","title":"부족한 금액 계산하기","categories":"스터디 알고리즘","author":"웅스노트","emoji":"💡"},"fields":{"slug":"/study/programmers/weekly-challenge-01/"}},"prev":{"id":"db40c0f3-6bf0-51e8-a5d4-c59d928b278c","html":"<h2 id=\"test\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#test\" aria-label=\"test permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>test</h2>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 14, 2022","title":"영화 리뷰 어플리케이션","categories":"스터디","author":"웅스노트","emoji":"📽️"},"fields":{"slug":"/study/sparta-web/"}},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://woongsnote.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":""}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/review/sparta-app/","nextSlug":"/study/programmers/weekly-challenge-01/","prevSlug":"/study/sparta-web/"}},
